title: Ep. 451 - Trump’s High Crime: Hurt Feelings
description:
Democrats in the mainstream media and Congress all the way to former presidents throw cold water on the impeachment push. We examine the latest “bombshell” testimony to parse what if anything this is all about. Then, Kanye West spreads the gospel to megachurch pastor Joel Osteen, Pope Francis wants to make pollution a sin, and a dark horse Democratic candidate takes a big lead in Iowa! Date: 11-18-2019
